Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class BoardProxy

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.Observable<BoardProxy>
it.polimi.ingsw.model.BoardProxy
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class BoardProxy
extends Observable<BoardProxy>
implements java.io.Serializable
This class acts as a proxy of the model's Board: it contains all the Board's information to display it properly and some other infos about the match in general. As the PlayerCommand, the BoardProxy is the only type of object that the server sends to the client
Author:
Marco Re, Elia Ravella
See Also:
PlayerCommand, Board, Serialized Form
